  "body": "[comment]: # (Please replace ... with your information. Remove < and >)\r\n\r\n### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want to know when problems are preventing me from sending or receiving messages so that I can wait or take other action\r\n\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Feature or Bug? i.e Type: Bug)\r\n*Type*: Feature\r\n\r\nErrors such as being offline or mail server issues prevent users from chatting. Therefore we should clearly surface these to inform the user. \r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n[comment]: # (Describe what you expected to happen.)\r\n\r\nWhen a user can't send or receive messages, they should know the state. The user can either wait or take action (eg, connect to wifi)\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n[comment]: # (Describe what happened.)\r\n\r\nWhen a user can't send or receive messages, they have no idea of the state and can get frustrated.\r\n\r\n\r\n### Solution\r\n\r\nTodo: designs.",
